snippet.title: Smells Like Burnt Rubber - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for a fast-paced, adrenaline-fueled racing experience with Smells Like Burnt Rubber. Choose your car, customize it, and hit the track in this intense arcade-style game.

Play with up to 4 friends in Splitscreen or join the Online Multiplayer. Are you ready to burn some rubber? 

Get it on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2194840/Smells_Like_Burnt_Rubber/

---
Music by: Repellent
Title: Asylum
Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/intl-de/artist/6yEXxCnGqXG3acdQ6IHKOA
